name: Proembrion (Krzysztof Syruc), Parametric Octocomblock-building process
description: A sequence of 64 outputs from the each step of the process of writing the right formula to create parametric compositions of colored blocks modularly representing a sequence of natural numbers - the images used to create 256 Octocomblocks and many more animations minted in 2021 on Hicetnunc.
